	<h1 class="title">免费互联网服务被叫停，扎克伯格和印度政府究竟在争什么？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99037/small/99037.jpg?1428742661" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">钟舒婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-29 18:13:17 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19894/medium/19894.jpg?1451363305" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


